{"tid":686583,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"諗住放榜之後報電競, 點知俾人打鑊勁","createTime":"2018-06-01T11:51:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T12:53:43.000Z","uid":4880,"like":19,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"901c548da77367d571e14be14f47f43f66f15c3f","tid":686583,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:51:57.000Z","msg":"話曬家下打機開下台每個月都有幾皮啦, 都唔明D廢老點諗<br />\n<br />\n岩先食飯果陣同老竇講<br />\n<br />\n我 = <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  老竇 = <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我: 我諗住遲下去港大讀書<br />\n佢: 咁咪幾好囉, 咁我都可以同班親戚有個交待<br />\n我: 但係讀電競你點睇?<br />\n佢嬲嬲地: 電乜撚野競啊<br />\n我: 而家果果都走去打機賺錢架啦, 閒閒地都幾皮一個月啦<br />\n佢拎住支筷子指住我: 打機賺錢你屎都冇得食<br />\n<br />\n講完就開鳩我拖, 跟手剪埋上網線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下各位ching 我應唔應該報警"},{"pid":"1db65fce0f8a1c922d3b1845c965ae4224612c0e","tid":686583,"uid":82929,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:55:06.000Z","msg":"報警啦<br />\n有d咁嘅老豆，真係家門不幸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06402fc3922ec20835f81060f9fc01602acdb39","tid":686583,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1db65fce0f8a1c922d3b1845c965ae4224612c0e","tid":686583,"uid":82929,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:55:06.000Z","msg":"報警啦<br />\n有d咁嘅老豆，真係家門不幸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:56:06.000Z","msg":"真係痴鳩線架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78be1fc23cc0f11a529743ceec8bfe7cbed5372","tid":686583,"uid":134958,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:56:26.000Z","msg":"你同佢講喺港大讀太空就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"977de9f6f34d6f5fb4e9b9c93621534277c65a61","tid":686583,"uid":3